WEBVTT

00:00:00.720 --> 00:00:04.520
There are a few things
that all of us need.

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:08.680
We all need air to breathe.

00:00:09.320 --> 00:00:11.696
We need clean water to drink.

00:00:11.720 --> 00:00:14.736
We need food to eat.
We need shelter and love.

00:00:14.760 --> 00:00:16.920
You know. Love is great, too.

00:00:18.360 --> 00:00:21.856
And we all need a safe place to pee.

00:00:21.880 --> 00:00:23.656
(Laughter) Yeah?

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:27.616
As a trans person who doesn't fit neatly
into the gender binary,

00:00:27.640 --> 00:00:30.120
if I could change the world tomorrow